{{Quote|Sector Four needs reinforcements. We are being overrun. Repeat, we are&mdash;|Fordo during the [[Battle of Coruscant/Legends|Battle of Coruscant]]|<ref name="Clone Wars Chapter 23">{{CW|23}}</ref>}}
'''Sector Four''' was a district on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. During the [[Battle of Coruscant/Legends|Battle of Coruscant]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Fordo]] and his team defended the plaza from [[Droid/Legends|droid]] fire, but were overrun. Fordo ordered the troopers to fall back, but [[Jedi Master/Legends|Master]] [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] soon arrived and countermanded those orders. [[Mace Windu/Legends|Mace Windu]] managed to control a captured [[Droid starfighter/Legends|droid starfighter]] and provide support for the dwindling forces.

